                <h3>Check out the Six Flags amusement park</h3>

                <p class="text-justify">Chicago's Six Flags amusement park has been open for a very long time and is quite well-liked. The largest rollercoaster is the most well-known of its more than 100 rides. It also includes the Raging Bull, the Batman ride, and the Joker free-fly coaster. There are other activities to participate in, such as the Halloween challenge and the coffin challenge. This amusement park in the White City has got to be the best of its kind. Also, November is generally crowded with visitors at this park. </p>

